code: @Override protected NodeInfo<IsNull> info() {     return NodeInfo.create(this, IsNull::new, field()). }
@Override protected IsNull replaceChild(Expression newChild) {     return new IsNull(source(), newChild). }
@Override public Object fold() {     return field().fold() == null || DataTypes.isNull(field().dataType()). }
@Override public String processScript(String script) {     return Scripts.formatTemplate(Scripts.SQL_SCRIPTS + ".isNull(" + script + ")"). }
@Override public UnaryScalarFunction negate() {     return new IsNotNull(source(), field()). }
